1) Why we cannot automate CAPTCHA using selenium?

CAPTCHA is designed specifically to block automation, including tools like Selenium.
CAPTCHA is made to check if a user is human
Selenium is a bot tool, not a human
CAPTCHA shows random images or text, so Selenium cannot understand them
Websites also detect bots and block them

